subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Na Yeon Choi shot a six-under-par 66 to take a one-stroke lead over Morgan Pressel and Karrie Webb after the first round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s season-ending Titleholders in Orlando, Fla.
